Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: A surfeit of scandal
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xv05
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Jul 1987
The James Bond-style story emerging from the Iran-Contra hearings may be too much to believe. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less